---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About ReguMe - Health Protocol Organizer" 
  description="Learn about ReguMe, the health protocol organizer for the social media age."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About ReguMe</h1>

    <p class="subtitle">
      Health Protocol Organizer for the Social Media Age
    </p>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>The Problem</h2>
      <p>
        Health advice is scattered across TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube. Influencers share 
        supplement stacks, morning routines, and wellness protocols—but keeping track of it all 
        is overwhelming. Screenshots pile up, notes get lost, and consistency becomes impossible.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>The Solution</h2>
      <p>
        ReguMe transforms social media wellness content into actionable, organized health protocols. 
        Simply paste a video URL, and our AI extracts the protocol and organizes it into:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Daily action checklists</strong> - Never forget a step</li>
        <li><strong>Supplement schedules</strong> - Track what to take and when</li>
        <li><strong>Habit reminders</strong> - Build consistency</li>
        <li><strong>Progress tracking</strong> - See what's working</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>How It Works</h2>

    <div class="step-grid">
      <div class="card step-card">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <h4>Import</h4>
        <p>Paste a video URL from TikTok, Instagram, YouTube, or Facebook</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card step-card">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <h4>Extract</h4>
        <p>AI analyzes the video and extracts the health protocol</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card step-card">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <h4>Organize</h4>
        <p>Protocols are saved to your personal library</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card step-card">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <h4>Track</h4>
        <p>Daily reminders keep you consistent</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Mission</h2>

    <div class="card mission-card">
      <p>
        <strong>Democratize health knowledge</strong> by making wellness protocols accessible, 
        organized, and actionable for everyone.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Our Values</h2>

    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="card value-card">
        <h3>Attribution</h3>
        <p>Always credit original creators</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card value-card">
        <h3>Safety</h3>
        <p>Strong medical disclaimers and user protection</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card value-card">
        <h3>Privacy</h3>
        <p>Your health data stays secure</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card value-card">
        <h3>Community</h3>
        <p>Share insights to help others</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Key Features</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>AI Video Extraction</h3>
      <p>Extract wellness protocols from TikTok, Instagram, YouTube, and Facebook videos using advanced AI (GPT-4o, Claude 3.5 Sonnet).</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Smart Folder Organization</h3>
      <p>Organize protocols into 12 pre-made categories (Sleep & Energy, Mental Health, Gut Health, etc.) or create custom folders.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Daily Action Tracking</h3>
      <p>Convert protocols into daily checklists, track completion, and build streaks with reminders.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Supplement Safety Scanner</h3>
      <p>Analyze supplement combinations for potential interactions and safety concerns (informational only - not medical advice).</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Outcome Tracking</h3>
      <p>Opt-in to anonymously track what protocols actually work, contributing to "democracy in health" insights.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Technology</h2>

    <p>Built with modern health tech stack:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>React Native + Expo</strong> - Native mobile experience</li>
      <li><strong>Supabase</strong> - Secure backend infrastructure</li>
      <li><strong>OpenAI GPT-4o & Whisper</strong> - AI-powered protocol extraction and transcription</li>
      <li><strong>Claude 3.5 Sonnet</strong> - Fallback AI processing</li>
      <li><strong>Apify</strong> - Video metadata extraction</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="alert alert-warning">
      <h3>⚕️ Important Medical Disclaimer</h3>
      <p>
        ReguMe provides informational content only and is not a substitute for professional 
        medical advice. Always consult with qualified healthcare providers before following 
        any health protocols.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="/medical-disclaimer">Read our full Medical Disclaimer →</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Get Started</h2>

    <div class="card" style="text-align: center; background: var(--background);">
      <h3>Join thousands organizing their wellness journey with ReguMe</h3>
      <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        <a href="#download" class="btn">Download on the App Store</a>
      </div>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0; color: var(--text-light); font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 2.5vw, 0.9375rem);">
        Questions? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a> or check our <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

